stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending : 任务创建
    pending --> running : 开始执行
    running --> completed : 执行成功
    running --> failed : 执行出错
    running --> killed : 被强制终止
    completed --> [*]
    failed --> [*]
    killed --> [*]
    
    note right of killed
        killed = 主动干预（用户/系统停止）
        failed = 执行出错
        两者共同构成"不正常终端状态"
    end note
